    • Reservation

      public Reservation​(java.lang.String code, java.lang.String flightCode, java.lang.String name, java.lang.String airline, java.lang.String citizenship, double cost, boolean active)
      Initializes each parameter inside of Reservation with active parameter.
      Parameters:
      code - The reservation code will be generated when a reservation is created.
      flightCode - The flight code the reservation is for.
      airline - The airline who owns and operates the flight.
      name - The name of the traveler.
      citizenship - The citizenship of the traveler.
      cost - The cost of the reservation.
      active - Whether the reservation is active or not.
